  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7, then before you start cooking, take your <strong>chicken</strong> out of the fridge, open the packet and let it air</p><p>Dust your work surface with a generous sprinkling of <strong>flour</strong></p><p>Unwrap your <strong>puff pastry</strong> and roll it out to approx. 0.5cm thickness with a <strong>rolling pin</strong>, then using a small bowl as a guide, cut the <strong>rolled pastry </strong>into 1 circle per person</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1716468688867-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1716468688867-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1716468688867-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1716468688867-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1716468688867-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>pastry circle[s]</strong> to a <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined baking tray (or two!) and score a 1cm border around the edge of the pastry with a knife, then score the pastry circle[s] inside the border in a criss-cross pattern</p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 15 min or until puffed up, golden and cooked through</p><p>Once cooked, set aside – this is your <strong>vol-au-vent</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1716468692822-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1716468692822-x400.jpg",
