    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Peel and dice your <strong>brown onion[s]</strong> finely</p><p>Top, tail, peel and dice your <strong>carrot[s]</strong> finely</p><p>Slice your <strong>baby button mushrooms</strong> finely</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
