      "instruction": "<p>Wash your<strong> salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper </p><p>Add the <strong>salad</strong> to a bowl with your <strong>white wine vinegar </strong>and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong> and toss – this is your <strong>dressed salad</strong></p>",
