      "instruction": "<p>To serve, carefully slice the scored top off the <strong>vol-au-vent</strong> using the border as a guide, then push down the inside</p><p>Spoon the <strong>chicken stew</strong> inside the<strong> vol-au-vent base</strong> and top with the <strong>vol-au-vent lid</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>chips </strong>and <strong>dressed salad </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
